      "end": 45.060001373291016,
      "text": "And my wife says, why we doing this",
      "start": 42.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 46.41999816894531,
      "text": "And why are we doing this",
      "start": 45.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 47.619998931884766,
      "text": "Are you hurting ourselves",
      "start": 46.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 49.65999984741211,
      "text": "And our son said, why are we doing this",
      "start": 47.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 52.91999816894531,
      "text": "Cause when you see me rocking in my way",
      "start": 49.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 54.959999084472656,
      "text": "Don't stare, don't stare",
      "start": 52.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 61.040000915527344,
      "text": "I can't believe you're treating our love like this",
      "start": 55.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 63.619998931884766,
      "text": "And now you don't remember all the joy",
      "start": 61.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 65.91999816894531,
      "text": "All, all the joy we had",
      "start": 63.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 69.12000274658203,
      "text": "And everything that felt so right",
      "start": 66.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 71.36000061035156,
      "text": "And now you're like, fuck that",
      "start": 69.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 75.12000274658203,
      "text": "I don't even wanna have a fight in anymore",
      "start": 71.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 82,
      "text": "Why, why you running away with the lies",
      "start": 76.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 84.16000366210938,
      "text": "Don't run and hide",
      "start": 82
    },
    {
      "end": 88.9800033569336,
      "text": "Come on, don't run and hide",
      "start": 85
    },
    {
      "end": 92.5999984741211,
      "text": "Run away",
      "start": 91.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 97.5999984741211,
      "text": "Run away in the night",
      "start": 93.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 100.37999725341797,
      "text": "When I, when I needed to most",
      "start": 97.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 102.69999694824219,
      "text": "To like, just a toast",
      "start": 100.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 106.05999755859375,
      "text": "But we took it away, it wasn't what we ought to be getting",
      "start": 102.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 108.73999786376953,
      "text": "But we started over, we did the song",
      "start": 106.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 112.22000122070312,
      "text": "Made the album, then we had to fall",
      "start": 109.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 121.94000244140625,
      "text": "Had to fall, and now we're divided",
      "start": 116.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 124.54000091552734,
      "text": "So baby, let me tell you",
      "start": 122.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 127.77999877929688,
      "text": "When you see me rocking in my way",
      "start": 124.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 130.74000549316406,
      "text": "Don't you stare too much, no",
      "start": 127.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 133.6999969482422,
      "text": "Don't stare, cause I'm balling and I'm falling",
      "start": 130.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 137.1199951171875,
      "text": "And I'm flying over the moon, yeah",
      "start": 133.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 141.36000061035156,
      "text": "Don't stare when you see me rolling my way",
      "start": 137.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 145.55999755859375,
      "text": "It could've been him, could've been us",
      "start": 141.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 149.74000549316406,
      "text": "Could've been, just a",
      "start": 146.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 152.13999938964844,
      "text": "Stereotype, stereotype",
      "start": 150.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 155.1999969482422,
      "text": "Denied if I slay, racist stereotype",
      "start": 152.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 156.9600067138672,
      "text": "I know you're broke, freaking dead",
      "start": 155.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 158.4600067138672,
      "text": "I know the river of truth",
      "start": 156.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 163.4199981689453,
      "text": "I know you, even though you don't think you do",
      "start": 158.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 173.82000732421875,
      "text": "Even though you don't think you do",
